ed="T" n="0758a02"/><persName key="A009309">釋道俊</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000027764">江陵</placeName>人也。住<placeName key="PL000000027054"><placeName>枝江</placeName><placeName>碧㵎精舍</placeName></placeName>，修<placeName key="PL000000028109">東<lb
ed="T" n="0758a03"/>山</placeName>無生<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1368"/>法門，即<persName key="A003654">信</persName>、<persName key="A000237">忍</persName>二祖號其所化之法也。<lb
ed="T" n="0758a04"/>勤潔苦行，跡不出<ref type="place" target="#PL000000027054">寺</ref>，經四十餘載。室邇人遠，<lb
ed="T" n="0758a05"/>莫敢請謁者，唯事杜默<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1383"/>。如是聲聞于天，<persName key="A002099">天<lb
ed="T" n="0758a06"/>后</persName>、<persName key="A002100">中宗</persName>二朝崇重高行之僧，<persName key="A009309">俊</persName>同<persName key="A008970">恒景</persName>，應<lb
ed="T" n="0758a07"/>詔入內供養。至<date notBefore-iso="+0707-10-09" key="j19795671980570" notAfter-iso="+0710-07-08"><name>景龍</name>中</date>求還故鄉，<ref type="person" target="#A002100">帝</ref>賜<lb
ed="T" n="0758a08"/>御製詩，并<persName key="A009306">奘</persName>、<persName key="A008970">景</persName>同歸<placeName key="PL000000027065">枝江</placeName>，卒于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000027054">本寺</ref>焉。</p>
